<materialsCitation id="B5B93CF3442FFFE7B429FDE5B628669B" ID-GBIF-Occurrence="3785680302" pageId="2" pageNumber="297">“Sahara algérien: Gardaia (Mzab)” (= Ghardaia, c.480 km south of Algiers, Algeria)</materialsCitation>
